---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { InspectNav } from '@/components/InspectNav';
import { loadBoard, loadAdrCount } from '@/lib/derived';
import { loadAdrCatalog } from '@/lib/content';

const board = loadBoard();
const adrCount = loadAdrCount();
const adrCatalog = loadAdrCatalog();
const recentAdrs = adrCatalog.slice(0, 3);

const REPO = 'https://github.com/nino-chavez/blueprint-platform/blob/main';
---
<Layout title="Inspect" description="Look under the hood. Methodology, substrate, derived state.">
  <header class="mb-6 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-contrast-500">Inspect</p>
    <h1 class="mb-3 font-heading text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight">
      Look under the hood.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">
      Methodology, Hive substrate, ADR-derived decisions, derived state authority. How the work happens — same care visible everywhere.
    </p>
  </header>

  <InspectNav currentPath={Astro.url.pathname} />

  <section class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <a href={`${REPO}/METHODOLOGY.md`} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group block rounded-lg border border-contrast-200 bg-background p-5 transition-colors hover:border-brand/60">
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground group-hover:text-brand">Methodology</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">Dual-track agile, five-actor model, two substrates. The long-term canon.</p>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide text-contrast-400">→ METHODOLOGY.md (8 sections)</p>
    </a>

    <a href={`${REPO}/WAYS-OF-WORKING.md`} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group block rounded-lg border border-contrast-200 bg-background p-5 transition-colors hover:border-brand/60">
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground group-hover:text-brand">Ways of working</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">Right-now operational layer — proposal taxonomy, cadence, spec-change rule. Time-boxed: sunsets when METHODOLOGY §4a is built.</p>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide text-contrast-400">→ WAYS-OF-WORKING.md</p>
    </a>

    <a href="https://github.com/nino-chavez/blueprint-platform/issues" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group block rounded-lg border border-contrast-200 bg-background p-5 transition-colors hover:border-brand/60">
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground group-hover:text-brand">Hive substrate</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">{board.totalOpen} open · {board.totalClosed} closed. Proposal lifecycle derived from GitHub state per ADR-0055.</p>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide text-contrast-400">→ GitHub Issues</p>
    </a>

    <a href={`${REPO}/docs/decisions`} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group block rounded-lg border border-contrast-200 bg-background p-5 transition-colors hover:border-brand/60">
      <h3 class="mb-1 font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground group-hover:text-brand">Decision record</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">{adrCount} ADRs, indexed by synthesis ID. Most recent:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-1">
        {recentAdrs.map((adr) => (
          <li class="truncate font-mono text-[11px] text-contrast-500">
            <span class="text-brand">ADR-{String(adr.number).padStart(4, '0')}</span>
            <span class="ml-1.5">{adr.title.replace(/^ADR-\d+:?\s*/i, '')}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 rounded-lg border border-contrast-200 bg-background p-5">
    <h3 class="mb-3 font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">Trust axioms</h3>
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">Three principles for how artifacts behave under multi-agent pressure. Ratified 2026-05-13 via synthesis #574. Full text in <a href={`${REPO}/METHODOLOGY.md#8-trust-axioms-ratified-2026-05-13-via-synthesis-574-close-out`} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-brand hover:underline">METHODOLOGY §8</a>.</p>
    <ol class="space-y-2">
      <li class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="shrink-0 font-mono text-xs text-contrast-400">8.1</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-foreground"><strong>State derives from code, not from docs.</strong> The authoritative answer to "what is our current state?" is always the codebase, never any document.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="shrink-0 font-mono text-xs text-contrast-400">8.2</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-foreground"><strong>Canonical-vs-derived ontology.</strong> Every doc is either source-of-truth (canonical) or commentary that decays (derived). Frontmatter contract enforces the distinction.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="shrink-0 font-mono text-xs text-contrast-400">8.3</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-foreground"><strong>Audit docs decay fast — snapshots, never authority.</strong> Claims about current state must reference a derivation ID, not prose. Re-derive before propagating any prior audit.</span>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 rounded-lg border border-contrast-200 bg-background p-5">
    <h3 class="mb-2 font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">Live substrate state</h3>
    <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">
      Real-time presence, activity stream, and reaction interactions against the Hive MCP backend live separately — it's an interactive app, not a static derived view. Portal already covers the snapshot data (see Gate status, Dependencies, and <a href="/roadmap" class="text-brand hover:underline">Roadmap</a>); the dashboard adds the live + interactive bits.
    </p>
    <a href="https://subs-hive-dashboard.pages.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-baseline gap-2 rounded-md border border-contrast-300 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-foreground transition-colors hover:border-brand hover:text-brand">
      Open hive dashboard <span aria-hidden>↗</span>
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
